folder: Alice Court & Atlantic Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
2 to 18 Alice Court, east side, north from Atlantic Avenue. Alice Court is a short, dead-end street, running north 150 feet from Atlantic Avenue.
September 13, 1940
P. L. Sperr
title: Brooklyn: Alice Court - Atlantic Avenue

folder: Atlantic Avenue & Alice Court, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Atlantic Avenue, north side, east from Alice Court. View 2 shows the north side of Atlantic Avenue, viewing eastward across Alice Court, the point of vantage being between Kingston Avenue and Alice Court.
September 13, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
